nium/media/icon/mailed-fist.svg","data":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p>The dragon exhales magical force energy in a 30-foot cone. Each creature in that area must make a DC <span class=\"rd__dc\">15</span> Constituion saving throw, taking 35 ([[/r 10d6]]) force damage on a failed save, or half as much damage on a successful one. On a failed save, creatures hit lose spellslots totalling [[/r 1d4 + 1]] levels (starting with the lowest). Any concentration check resulting from this damage is made with disadvantage.</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"DHC","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":30,"width":null,"units":"ft","type":"cone"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"other","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["10d6","force"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"con","dc":15,"scaling":"flat"},"requirements":"","recharge":{"value":5,"charged":true}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"lCTxyQknjbpx8AZr":3},"flags":{}},{"_id":"kW681BU5r9w7z10X","name":"Spell Absorbtion","type":"feat","img":"modules/plutonium/media/icon/mighty-force.svg","data":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p>Amethyst dragons can absorb spells. Young amethyst dragons can store a single absorbed spell in his body. If the dragon currently has no spell absorbed, he can use his Absorption ability when he is targeted or inside the area of effect of an area spell. The spellcaster has to make a DC <span class=\"rd__dc\">15</span> spellcasting ability check. If the spellcaster fails the ability check, the spell is absorbed, otherwise the spell resolves normally.</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div><p>Any currently absorbed spell should be visible to any creature looking at the dragon, e.g. by having magical vines or an exploding minitiature fireball inside a gem of his snout</p><p>Spell Usage. Amethys dragons can use absorbed spells. The dragon can trigger a similar effect to the absorbed spell on his next bite attack that hits a creature. The exact effect is in the DMs discretion, but should mimic the spell effect and uses the DC and level of the absorbed spell.</p><p>Examples are:</p><p>- @spell[Entangle]: The next bite attack forces the creature hit to make a strength saving throw or be @condition[restrained] by vines.</p><p>- @spell[Fireball] : The mouth of the dragon errupts in a fiery explosion, and every creature in the area is subjected to the fireball effect.</p><p>- @spell[Magic Missile] : Three glowing darts of magical force hit the bitten creature in addition to the normal effects of the bite attack</p><p>The amethyst dragon is immune to all area effects of spells triggered by this ability</p></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"DHC","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null},"consume":{"type":null,"target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"other","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"flat"},"requirements":"","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"lCTxyQknjbpx8AZr":3},"flags":{}},{"_id":"5lgss1zA2D4ba0Yu","name":"Multiattack","type":"feat","img":"icons/skills/melee/blade-tips-triple-steel.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p>The dragon makes three attacks: one with its bite and two with its claws.</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inl